# Version Information

## Provider Version
- **Current**: 0.7.5-dev
- **Previous Release**: 0.7.4
- **Purpose**: Development version for testing CloudDNS stable identifiers feature

## SDK Version
- **go.anx.io/go-anxcloud**: v0.9.2-alpha
- **Previous**: v0.9.1-alpha

## Installation Path
~/.terraform.d/plugins/hashicorp.com/anexia-it/anxcloud/0.7.5-dev/linux_amd64/terraform-provider-anxcloud

## Build Command
```bash
make install
```

This will:
1. Build the provider binary
2. Install it to the correct plugin directory
3. Make it available to Terraform with version 0.7.5-dev
